org.intermine.biovalidator.api

Class ValidatorHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.biovalidator.api.ValidatorHelper

  • public final class ValidatorHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides helper methods create validator. Example: 1. ValidatorHelper.validate("file", "fasta-dna", false) 2. Or Simply: ValidatorHelper.validateFastaDna("file")
